e.\n300 Negro, White\nWorkers in Protest\nOver 300 Negro and white work- I\ners attended a Protest meeting at\nRoyal Circle Hall, Sunday after- j\nnoon, his meeting was called by\nthe Communist Party in response to j\nthe recent wave of mob terrorism j\ndirected against the Negro and\nwhite workers.\nALL\nPartv Members\nThat have been assigned\nReport\nfor\nRED ft\nSunday J\nTHIS SUNDAY\nJune 1, 1930\nfor work in the present jjj\nCirculation Campaign of the\nBaity i\u00a3lXbri*r\nReport, to your\nSECTION HEADQUARTERS\nSection 1\u201427 East 4th St. N.Y.C,\nSection 2\u20141179 Broadway, N. Y. C.\nSection 3\u20141179 Broadway, N. Y. C.\nSection 4\u2014308 Lenox Ave., N. Y. C.\nSection 5\u2014569 Prospect Ave, Bx.\nSection 6\u201468 Whipple St., Blyn.\nSection 7\u2014136-15th Street, Bklyn.\nSection B\u2014los Thatfqrd St., Bklyn.\nj \u201cFor All Kinds of Insurance\"\nfARL BRODSKV\n\\/Te!ephone: Murray Rill KSM JL\n7 East 42nd Street, New York\n\n_ _\nI Ur. ABRAHAM MARKOFF\nSURGEON DENTIST\n240 EAST 113th STREET\nCor. Second Ave. New York\nDAILY EXCEPT FRIDAY\nPlease telephone for appointment\nTelephones Lehigh 6022\ni I-\nTel. OKChard 3783\nDR. L. KESSLER\nSURGEON DENTIST\nStrictly by Appointment\n4S-5C DELANCEY STREET\nCor. Eldridge St. NEW YORK\n|DR. J. MINDEL\nSURGEON I>2NTIST\n1 UNION SQUARE\nRcom 803\u2014Phon\u00ab: Algonquin lilt\nNot tonnected with any\nothsr office\nAll Comrades Meet at\nBRONSTEIN\u2019S\nVegetarian Health\nRestaurant\n558 Claremont Parkway, Bronx\nRATIONALES\nVegetarian 1\u00a7 I\nRESTAURANT f j\n199 SECOND AVELUE 1\nBat. IStb and lStb Bta. 4? 1\nStrictly Vegetarian Food\nr\u2014MELROSE^\nIN- VEGETARIAN\nuairy restaurant\nComrade, will Alwara flai I*\nPlea.ant to lilaa at Oar Plaea.\n1787 SOUTHERN BLVD., Bronx\n(near 174th 8L Station)\nPHONE:\u2014 INTERVALS 1141.\nj\nHEALTH FOOD\nVegetarian\nRESTAURANT\n1600 MADISON AY*.\nPhone: UNlveralty 586*\nVfj\nPbona: Sturreaant Ml* \"T| j\nJohn\u2019s Restaurant j\nSPECIALTY! ITALIAN DIMH\nA plaoa w